                                    BUS RESERVATION
                                ----------------------
                                ---------------------- 

    This program is for BUS reservation. Which provide below funcationality.
    
    1>> Sign In
    2>> Sign Up
    3>> Exit

  >>>>  It check that is user exiting user or new user ?
        According to that it takes some decisions.
        
  >>>>  It encripted the user cradiantials and then store into file.as a security
        feature.


  >>>>  If Exsiting user then ask for user cradintial and check with Data base.
        Else make a profile for user and again ask provided Cradintial.

  >>>>  It asks user to enter how many seats they want.If avaible then enter
        their details and store into their data base(DB).

  >>>>  Program ask to Enter NAME,AGE and GENDER and store that into DB.
       




                   ---------------------------  
        >>>>>>>    FILE name and their purpose    <<<<<<      
                   --------------------------- 



        
        1->>    main.c 
                    >>>> main file from where pogram start.

        2->>    headerfiles.h
                    >>>> In this file all the funcations prototypes and structs declares
                         some variable like cnt and Macroes define and declare.

        3->>    front_page.c
                    >>>> This file basically deals with the starting face of program.



